            <title><![CDATA[Rose & Camellia Collection ‘Online Battle Mode’ update launches June 22]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/rose-camellia-collection-online-battle-mode-update-launches-june-22</link>
            <guid>1556920</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Unleash a magnificent and intense slap duel.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>The online battle mode update for slap battle action game <em><a title="Games > Rose &amp; Camellia Collection [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/rose-camellia-collection">Rose &amp; Camellia Collection</a></em> will launch on June 22, publisher <a title="Companies > PLAYISM [348 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/playism">PLAYISM</a> and developer Nigoro announced. <span id="more-1060284"></span></p><p>“With the implementation of online battles, the destined slap battles against the world’s strongest players are about to begin,” PLAYISM said. “Let your elegant fighting spirit reside in your hands, and unleash a magnificent and intense slap duel!”</p><p><em>Rose &amp; Camellia Collection</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>.</p><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>“Online Battle Mode” Update Release Date Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><iframe title="『薔薇と椿 ～お豪華絢爛版～』オンラインお対決モヲド～お電波通信対戦編～ 告知トレーラー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oMl7uUT7ZCc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe title="《薔薇與椿～豪華絢爛版～》線上對決模式：～電波通訊對戰之章～ 6月22日更新上線" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BYibPIkYCSM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/06/rose-camellia-collection-online-battle-mode-update-launches-june-22]]></content:encoded>
