    <p><span>DELTARUNE Chapter 5, DEAD OR ALIVE 6 Last Round, more.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><em><a title="Games > Star Fox (2026) [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/star-fox-2026">Star Fox</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, and <em><a title="Games > Villion: Code [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/villion-code">Villion: Code</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, Switch 2, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a> are the&nbsp;highlight of this week’s Japanese video game releases. <span id="more-1060273"></span></p><p>Also due out this week are <em><a title="Games > DELTARUNE [8 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/deltarune">DELTARUNE</a></em> Chapter 5 for PlayStation 5, Switch 2, PlayStation 4, Switch, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, <em><a title="Games > DEAD OR ALIVE 6 Last Round [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dead-or-alive-6-last-round">DEAD OR ALIVE 6 Last Round</a></em> for PlayStation 5, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and PC, and <em><a title="Games > Medabots Card Robattle RB [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/medabots-card-robattle-rb">Medabots Card Robattle RB</a></em> for Switch.</p><p>Get the full list of this week’s Japanese game releases below. It should be noted that <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">Gematsu</a> will receive a small percentage of money from purchases made through <a title="Companies > Playasia" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/playasia">Play-Asia</a> links. You can also save five percent with our multi-use “<strong>GEMATSU2025</strong>” coupon code.</p><h2><span>Physical and Digital</span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > Atomic Heart [19 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/atomic-heart">Atomic Heart</a>: Ultimate Edition</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/atomic-heart-ultimate-edition-multi-language/13/70jrpb?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>) – Already available worldwide.</li><li><em>Blackish House ←sideZ: Retour</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/blackish-house-sidez-retour-/13/70jn0v?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)<ul><li>Special Edition (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/en/blackish-house-sidez-retour-special-edition/13/70jn11?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li></ul><!-- AD: content -->
